      "date": "2013-01-11 22:01:13.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 6: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/131c9cc2-5c36-11e2-aa66-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
